                            <comment id="17231744" author="akettmann" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2020 18:38:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would definitely like to see the bigtable reader implemented if it can be. Had to write a dataflow job in Java, which is really not my strong suit to do half the work then I can do the rest in Python, simply due to the bigtable reader I wrote being a simple dumb ParDo.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
